278
00:22:24,676 --> 00:22:25,510
My voice?

279
00:22:27,012 --> 00:22:29,473
No, I'm not sick.

280
00:22:29,556 --> 00:22:31,016
I think it's just a cold.

281
00:22:33,977 --> 00:22:35,520
Were you just calling to check in?

282
00:22:36,521 --> 00:22:37,481
Okay.

283
00:22:38,231 --> 00:22:39,816
All right. See you later.

284
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:40,734
Bye.

285
00:22:57,542 --> 00:23:01,671
So please don't think about visiting
Ji Seung-kyu's mother at the hospital.

286
00:23:02,339 --> 00:23:04,382
You'll only receive public backlash.

287
00:23:23,693 --> 00:23:25,612
-Mom.
-Hey, Yoon-seo.

288
00:23:26,113 --> 00:23:28,073
Are you sick?

289
00:23:30,117 --> 00:23:32,702
Did you catch a cold?
Or is it something else?

290
00:23:32,786 --> 00:23:34,246
No, I'm fine.

291
00:23:34,329 --> 00:23:35,914
Did you eat?

292
00:23:35,997 --> 00:23:37,499
Yes. Are you hungry?

293
00:23:37,582 --> 00:23:39,209
I already ate.

294
00:23:39,292 --> 00:23:40,502
Should I get you some medicine?

295
00:23:40,585 --> 00:23:41,878
That's okay.

296
00:23:42,629 --> 00:23:44,965
-Mom, don't be sick.
-Yes?

297
00:23:45,048 --> 00:23:48,927
-Okay?
-I'm not sick. I'm totally fine.

298
00:23:49,010 --> 00:23:50,637
Are you sure?

299
00:24:16,121 --> 00:24:17,205
How dare you?

300
00:24:18,957 --> 00:24:20,709
How dare you come here?

301
00:24:29,092 --> 00:24:30,677
You killed my son!

302
00:24:30,760 --> 00:24:32,637
Are you here to see
if his mother died as well?

303
00:24:32,721 --> 00:24:35,599
You have no right to come here,
you murderer!

304
00:24:41,271 --> 00:24:43,273
Say something, damn it.

305
00:24:43,356 --> 00:24:46,693
Why did you do that to Seung-kyu?

306
00:24:47,694 --> 00:24:49,905
Being an assemblyman
doesn't give you that right!

307
00:24:51,656 --> 00:24:52,991
Where's that badge of yours?

308
00:24:53,074 --> 00:24:54,159
What is it?

309
00:24:54,242 --> 00:24:56,369
Are you going to resign
for what you've done?

310
00:24:56,453 --> 00:24:57,287
Are you?

311
00:25:00,081 --> 00:25:01,333
I also

312
00:25:03,043 --> 00:25:04,461
lost my son recently.

313
00:25:07,130 --> 00:25:08,381
I'm not here today

314
00:25:10,217 --> 00:25:11,468
as an assemblyman.

315
00:25:13,261 --> 00:25:14,304
I'm here…

316
00:25:16,097 --> 00:25:17,265
as a father…

317
00:25:18,850 --> 00:25:20,268
who lost his son.

318
00:25:25,565 --> 00:25:26,483
Drop the act!

319
00:25:27,609 --> 00:25:31,071
No matter what you say,
it won't bring my son back.

320
00:25:31,571 --> 00:25:32,656
Answer me!

321
00:25:33,823 --> 00:25:36,076
Did he really deserve to die?

322
00:25:36,576 --> 00:25:37,994
Answer me!

323
00:25:42,374 --> 00:25:45,460
You killed my son!

324
00:25:46,670 --> 00:25:48,880
Let me go!

325
00:25:51,466 --> 00:25:53,468
Let me go!

326
00:26:09,276 --> 00:26:12,946
Don't come into my room or touch my stuff
without my permission. Understand?

327
00:26:34,342 --> 00:26:36,303
She gave it to me here,

328
00:26:37,846 --> 00:26:39,431
and I put it in my bag.

329
00:26:40,390 --> 00:26:42,100
Where the heck is it?

330
00:27:16,384 --> 00:27:18,720
YOUNGSAN
SESAME OIL

331
00:27:20,722 --> 00:27:23,308
I'm feeling unwell.
I need to get some rest.

332
00:27:37,113 --> 00:27:37,947
YOUNGSAN TO SEOUL

333
00:27:38,031 --> 00:27:38,865
Youngsan?

334
00:28:29,124 --> 00:28:32,001
COLD MEDICINE

335
