341
00:30:18,316 --> 00:30:19,692
That's okay.

342
00:30:19,776 --> 00:30:21,277
I'm going to head out.

343
00:30:26,366 --> 00:30:28,952
Right, Yoon-seo's class is
visiting the National Assembly today.

344
00:30:29,869 --> 00:30:31,996
Right. That was today.

345
00:30:34,415 --> 00:30:35,416
Hold on.

346
00:30:38,795 --> 00:30:40,338
You're not running a fever.

347
00:30:41,005 --> 00:30:44,092
You sounded sick yesterday,
and you look really pale right now.

348
00:30:45,301 --> 00:30:46,636
No, I'm okay.

349
00:30:48,096 --> 00:30:49,848
Don't just say that.
Go see a doctor later.

350
00:30:51,015 --> 00:30:52,058
Okay.

351
00:30:52,141 --> 00:30:53,685
All right. See you later.

352
00:31:20,837 --> 00:31:24,924
SEUNG-HEE: COME TO THIS ADDRESS AT 7 P.M.

353
00:31:57,832 --> 00:31:58,791
Come in.

354
00:32:02,086 --> 00:32:04,213
For breakfast and lunch…

355
00:32:06,591 --> 00:32:07,592
Right.

356
00:32:11,304 --> 00:32:12,847
I thought you forgot these.

357
00:32:12,931 --> 00:32:14,599
Did you bring these from my studio?

358
00:32:14,682 --> 00:32:15,725
Sorry?

359
00:32:15,808 --> 00:32:16,643
Yes.

360
00:32:17,602 --> 00:32:20,355
I stopped by last night
to look for my lip balm.

361
00:32:20,438 --> 00:32:22,273
-Lip balm?
-Yes, my lip balm.

362
00:32:23,983 --> 00:32:26,027
I saw the passcode
when you were opening the--

363
00:32:26,110 --> 00:32:27,570
What did I tell you?

364
00:32:27,654 --> 00:32:30,907
I told you not to go into my space
without my permission, didn't I?

365
00:32:37,789 --> 00:32:38,706
I'm sorry.

366
00:32:39,916 --> 00:32:42,210
I'm just a kid you know.
I shouldn't have gone into your space.

367
00:32:45,213 --> 00:32:46,214
But I only did so

368
00:32:47,548 --> 00:32:50,760
because you didn't keep
your promise about finding my lip balm.

369
00:32:55,807 --> 00:32:57,225
Aren't you taking these?

370
00:33:01,145 --> 00:33:02,230
Should I put them back?

371
00:33:02,313 --> 00:33:03,606
Or should I throw them away?

372
00:33:13,783 --> 00:33:15,159
There's a statue too.

373
00:33:15,243 --> 00:33:16,411
You're right.

374
00:33:17,495 --> 00:33:18,788
It's huge.

375
00:33:20,123 --> 00:33:21,040
Hello,

376
00:33:21,124 --> 00:33:23,376
