377
00:33:24,961 --> 00:33:26,546
-You're awesome!
-You're so handsome!

378
00:33:26,629 --> 00:33:28,548
-You're so amazing!
-It's nice to meet you!

379
00:33:28,631 --> 00:33:29,966
How do you like being here?

380
00:33:30,049 --> 00:33:31,926
-We love it!
-It's so nice!

381
00:33:32,010 --> 00:33:33,720
-You're so cool!
-You're amazing.

382
00:33:33,803 --> 00:33:34,762
Thank you.

383
00:34:40,536 --> 00:34:43,414
Hye-joo told you to bring this to me?
Why isn't she using it at home?

384
00:34:43,498 --> 00:34:44,832
I'm not sure.

385
00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:46,751
All right.

386
00:34:47,794 --> 00:34:50,046
It's all done.

387
00:35:01,432 --> 00:35:03,684
Have some kalguksu as well
next time, okay?

388
00:35:04,268 --> 00:35:06,562
Thank you. Goodbye.

389
00:35:06,646 --> 00:35:07,897
Bye.

390
00:35:08,397 --> 00:35:09,440
Pay up.

391
00:35:10,358 --> 00:35:11,567
You need to pay for that.

392
00:35:12,568 --> 00:35:14,445
Ms. Hyeon, she didn't pay.

393
00:35:14,946 --> 00:35:17,865
Hey, why are you leaving without--

394
00:35:18,699 --> 00:35:21,828
Come back for some kalguksu, okay?
Be careful not to spill that.

395
00:35:22,411 --> 00:35:23,579
