-Go on.

396
00:35:26,165 --> 00:35:28,584
FREE FOOD FOR CHILDREN, TEENAGERS,
AND PREGNANT WOMEN

397
00:35:32,421 --> 00:35:33,798
Have you had lunch?

398
00:35:37,051 --> 00:35:38,594
Hello, it's nice to meet you.

