00:35:39,512 --> 00:35:41,139
It's nice to meet you.

400
00:35:41,222 --> 00:35:42,098
Gosh.

401
00:35:43,099 --> 00:35:44,559
-This is so cool.
-Nice to meet you.

402
00:35:44,642 --> 00:35:46,561
-Your dad is so amazing.
-I'm going to frame this.

403
00:35:47,603 --> 00:35:48,437
See you at home.

404
00:35:49,939 --> 00:35:51,607
So you're Da-som.

405
00:35:51,691 --> 00:35:52,608
Hi.

406
00:35:52,692 --> 00:35:54,652
-Hello.
-It's nice to meet you.

407
00:35:56,487 --> 00:35:59,115
By the way,
is this really your personal number?

408
00:35:59,198 --> 00:36:01,242
Yes. Call that number, and I'll pick up.

409
00:36:01,325 --> 00:36:02,451
No way.

410
00:36:03,119 --> 00:36:04,370
Do you give dating advice?

411
00:36:04,453 --> 00:36:07,832
I'm sorry, but I only do that
on the weekends.

412
00:36:09,083 --> 00:36:10,126
Did you not have breakfast?

413
00:36:10,793 --> 00:36:12,170
Then you get an extra.

414
00:36:12,253 --> 00:36:13,379
Thank you.

415
00:36:18,426 --> 00:36:20,803
You didn't know how things work here,

416
00:36:20,887 --> 00:36:22,889
so I don't blame you,

417
00:36:24,432 --> 00:36:26,934
but it still bothers me

418
00:36:27,018 --> 00:36:28,686
that I couldn't explain it properly.

419
00:36:31,355 --> 00:36:33,316
Lots of kids are coming by today.

420
00:36:33,399 --> 00:36:35,067
-Really?
-Yes.

421
00:36:35,151 --> 00:36:39,780
I still wish more kids would stop by.

422
00:36:40,781 --> 00:36:43,910
Didn't you say Yoon-seo's grandmother
gave you dumplings for free?

423
00:36:43,993 --> 00:36:44,827
Yes.

424
00:36:46,329 --> 00:36:49,207
Whenever my mom was working late,

425
00:36:49,290 --> 00:36:52,501
I'd come here by myself
and ask for some dumplings.

426
00:36:54,295 --> 00:36:58,591
And when my mom would
hurry over to apologize and try to pay,

427
00:36:58,674 --> 00:37:01,510
she wouldn't take the money
and she'd say children had to eat well.

428
00:37:02,136 --> 00:37:05,681
And she would say
that's what neighbors are for.

429
00:37:08,226 --> 00:37:10,561
When I came back to this neighborhood

430
00:37:10,645 --> 00:37:12,897
and didn't know how to make ends meet,

431
00:37:14,523 --> 00:37:16,442
she gave me a job here.

432
00:37:17,068 --> 00:37:18,444
I was truly grateful.

433
00:37:19,779 --> 00:37:21,405
Had she been around a bit longer,

434
00:37:21,489 --> 00:37:23,824
she would have seen her son
become an assemblyman.

435
00:37:25,076 --> 00:37:26,327
Come to think of it,

436
00:37:26,410 --> 00:37:28,829
Assemblyman Nam must
take after his mother.

437
00:37:31,207 --> 00:37:34,168
Yeo-jin, can I take
a couple bottles of that oil home?

438
00:37:34,252 --> 00:37:35,670
Sure.

439
00:37:40,758 --> 00:37:41,842
OPTIMIZATION OF SEX CRIME VICTIM SUPPORT

440
00:37:41,926 --> 00:37:43,803
PENALTY AND VICTIM SUPPORT
FOR DIGITAL SEX CRIME

441
00:37:45,221 --> 00:37:46,222
Sir,

442
00:37:46,305 --> 00:37:48,808
I'm sure you know, as a member of
the Legislation and Judiciary Committee,

443
00:37:48,891 --> 00:37:52,645
but there hasn't been a single
proposed amendment regarding sex crimes

444
00:37:52,728 --> 00:37:55,856
that passed the committee's review
to be referred to the plenary session

445
00:37:56,357 --> 00:37:57,566
this year.

446
00:37:58,234 --> 00:38:01,362
With dozens of bills proposed every day
in the National Assembly,

447
00:38:01,445 --> 00:38:05,241
it makes sense that not every one
of them is discussed in depth.

448
00:38:06,617 --> 00:38:08,786
My term will be over in a few months.

449
00:38:09,870 --> 00:38:12,081
All bills that fail to be passed by then

450
00:38:12,915 --> 00:38:14,583
will automatically be disposed of.

451
00:38:15,084 --> 00:38:16,043
Right.

452
00:38:17,295 --> 00:38:19,755
If I'm being completely honest,

453
00:38:20,381 --> 00:38:23,592
unless a major case of sex crime occurs

454
00:38:24,343 --> 00:38:25,386
that brings about

455
00:38:26,137 --> 00:38:28,431
a great public uproar,

456
00:38:29,223 --> 00:38:32,685
it won't be easy to push ahead with a bill

457
00:38:33,519 --> 00:38:35,396
in merely six months.

458
00:38:36,439 --> 00:38:37,523
I agree with her.

459
00:38:37,606 --> 00:38:39,108
During Ji Seung-kyu's case,

460
00:38:39,817 --> 00:38:42,611
the public demanded
severe punishment for sex offenders…

461
00:38:42,695 --> 00:38:44,030
But it didn't last long.

462
00:38:45,197 --> 00:38:48,159
We live in Dynamic Korea
where we have a new headline every day.

463
00:38:49,285 --> 00:38:52,413
Sir, it's time for you
to visit the district office.

464
00:38:53,247 --> 00:38:54,206
Okay.

465
00:39:15,603 --> 00:39:16,645
Why are you still here?

466
00:39:17,521 --> 00:39:18,522
I haven't paid.

467
00:39:19,106 --> 00:39:19,982
Forget it.

468
00:39:20,066 --> 00:39:21,650
No, I want to pay.

469
00:39:21,734 --> 00:39:23,778
We don't charge pregnant women either.

470
00:39:23,861 --> 00:39:25,529
