with Ji-hoon's child?

474
00:39:33,829 --> 00:39:35,664
Although that's also true.

475
00:39:35,748 --> 00:39:36,582
Either way,

476
00:39:36,665 --> 00:39:40,002
I'm glad you can eat our dumplings
despite your morning sickness.

477
00:39:40,086 --> 00:39:42,671
Come by whenever you want.

478
00:39:45,424 --> 00:39:46,425
Okay.

