488
00:40:54,201 --> 00:40:55,661
-and drove away.
-My gosh.

489
00:40:55,744 --> 00:40:57,538
Do you know Ko Ji-seop
from the Daehan Party?

490
00:40:57,621 --> 00:40:59,832
Anyway, his wife drove off

491
00:40:59,915 --> 00:41:02,585
after running a man over and killing him.

492
00:41:03,502 --> 00:41:04,545
Oh, my.

493
00:41:05,045 --> 00:41:06,589
-They can't reach him right now.
-The police

494
00:41:06,672 --> 00:41:08,340
analyzed the CCTV footage…

495
00:41:09,508 --> 00:41:11,302
Of course I feel bad about the victim,

496
00:41:11,385 --> 00:41:14,221
but I'm worried about her husband.
He's a politician.

497
00:41:18,893 --> 00:41:21,270
Ms. Woo, please give us a comment
on the current situation.

498
00:41:34,533 --> 00:41:37,036
-Yes?
-Your car is waiting out front, sir.

499
00:41:37,119 --> 00:41:38,162
Okay, thank you.

500
00:41:43,459 --> 00:41:44,793
See you later.

501
00:41:52,676 --> 00:41:55,221
The wife of Assemblyman Ko Ji-seop
of the Daehan Party

502
00:41:55,304 --> 00:41:58,057
