-Goodbye.

507
00:42:09,318 --> 00:42:11,904
Do you really think
Assemblyman Ko didn't know?

508
00:42:11,987 --> 00:42:12,863
I'm not sure.

509
00:42:13,531 --> 00:42:16,825
They really need to
keep their family in line.

510
00:42:16,909 --> 00:42:19,328
Their careers could end
from one mistake by their family.

511
00:42:19,411 --> 00:42:20,829
Exactly.

512
00:42:23,958 --> 00:42:25,334
-Hello.
-Hello.

513
00:42:31,423 --> 00:42:32,967
ASSEMBLYMAN KO JI-SEOP

514
00:42:43,644 --> 00:42:45,187
