00:44:30,876 --> 00:44:31,752
Okay.

534
00:44:32,336 --> 00:44:33,796
You didn't reply to my texts,

535
00:44:34,380 --> 00:44:35,839
so I thought you weren't coming.

536
00:44:36,590 --> 00:44:37,591
So I thought,

537
00:44:38,384 --> 00:44:40,135
"Did she run away again?"

538
00:44:40,219 --> 00:44:42,346
"She's making things more interesting."

539
00:44:42,846 --> 00:44:46,517
No, I'm coming to Youngsan.

540
00:44:47,059 --> 00:44:48,394
I'll be there.

541
00:44:49,103 --> 00:44:51,480
All right. See you later.

542
00:45:02,241 --> 00:45:04,201
See that greenhouse over there?

543
00:45:04,284 --> 00:45:06,537
-You'd be buying that much.
-But we don't even know

544
00:45:06,620 --> 00:45:07,746
if the road will be built there.

545
00:45:07,830 --> 00:45:09,164
Goodness, ma'am.

546
00:45:09,248 --> 00:45:11,708
The price has already doubled
since last month.

547
00:45:11,792 --> 00:45:14,253
It'll skyrocket
if a road really gets built.

548
00:45:17,589 --> 00:45:20,134
You were taking so long
that I thought you left.

549
00:45:20,217 --> 00:45:22,010
Were you talking to your husband again?

550
00:45:22,803 --> 00:45:23,720
No.

551
00:45:23,804 --> 00:45:26,807
Gosh, she must be very happily married.

552
00:45:26,890 --> 00:45:27,808
Who cares?

553
00:45:28,308 --> 00:45:31,812
She's so happy with her husband
that she neglects her old mother.

554
00:45:31,895 --> 00:45:34,356
-Mom.
-Hey, I don't need you either.

555
00:45:34,440 --> 00:45:36,316
I'm going to meet my friends.

556
00:45:37,067 --> 00:45:38,235
So go to your husband.

557
00:45:41,447 --> 00:45:42,656
Mr. Park, let's go.

558
00:45:49,496 --> 00:45:51,790
-See you tomorrow.
-Bye.

559
00:45:51,874 --> 00:45:56,003
SONMAT NOODLES

560
00:46:03,969 --> 00:46:05,387
Hello, sir.

561
00:46:05,471 --> 00:46:07,014
-Hello.
-Hello.

562
00:46:07,097 --> 00:46:09,016
-I'm rooting for you.
-I appreciate it.

563
00:46:09,099 --> 00:46:10,309
-You can do it.
-Thank you.

564
00:46:19,776 --> 00:46:22,404
THE COMPETENT ASSEMBLYMAN!
WE BELIEVE IN YOU, NAM JOONG-DO

565
00:46:27,117 --> 00:46:28,243
Ma'am.

566
00:46:28,327 --> 00:46:30,120
Goodness, Assemblyman Nam.

567
00:46:31,622 --> 00:46:33,499
-Ma'am, what are you doing here?
-What the…

568
00:46:33,582 --> 00:46:35,292
-Well…
-Assemblyman Nam.

569
00:46:35,375 --> 00:46:36,585
Goodness.

570
00:46:36,668 --> 00:46:39,963
Ma'am, you're cleaning out here again?

571
00:46:40,047 --> 00:46:43,926
You should just come inside
and have some tea.

572
00:46:44,009 --> 00:46:49,306
I'm forever grateful to you,

573
00:46:49,389 --> 00:46:51,642
so I wanted to give you something,

574
00:46:51,725 --> 00:46:54,603
but they told me
you couldn't accept any gifts.

575
00:46:55,395 --> 00:46:57,981
There's nothing else I could do for you.

576
00:46:58,065 --> 00:47:02,778
It's no big deal, so don't worry about me.

577
00:47:04,738 --> 00:47:06,198
Sir.

578
00:47:06,281 --> 00:47:07,574
Oh, no.

579
00:47:07,658 --> 00:47:09,368
That's a dirty rag.

580
00:47:09,910 --> 00:47:11,870
Goodness. Sir.

581
00:47:12,579 --> 00:47:14,206
Thanks to you,

582
00:47:14,873 --> 00:47:16,875
that bastard got what he deserved.

583
00:47:17,668 --> 00:47:18,835
And now,

584
00:47:19,545 --> 00:47:22,047
I'm finally at peace.

585
00:47:23,257 --> 00:47:28,428
I'll repay your kindness at all costs.

586
00:47:29,846 --> 00:47:30,889
Thank you.

587
00:47:31,473 --> 00:47:33,100
Thank you so much.

588
00:47:33,976 --> 00:47:35,435
Thank you.

589
00:47:37,437 --> 00:47:38,981
Get home safely.

590
00:47:40,232 --> 00:47:41,608
Goodbye, ma'am.

591
00:47:50,993 --> 00:47:53,245
She doesn't know yet.

592
00:47:54,413 --> 00:47:56,498
That bastard uploaded the video

593
00:47:56,582 --> 00:47:58,250
right before he jumped.

594
00:47:59,710 --> 00:48:01,795
When the arrest warrant was applied for,

595
00:48:01,878 --> 00:48:03,505
he had only threatened to leak it.

596
00:48:03,589 --> 00:48:07,134
Then the case was closed
following his death.

597
00:48:07,217 --> 00:48:09,970
So no one knew about the leak
until later on.

598
00:48:12,097 --> 00:48:14,016
Has it spread widely?

599
00:48:14,891 --> 00:48:17,519
The police are still hunting down
whoever redistributes it.

600
00:48:17,603 --> 00:48:20,272
The specialist you personally hired

601
00:48:20,355 --> 00:48:22,649
is working to remove all the videos.

602
00:48:22,733 --> 00:48:26,778
But it's not easy to get rid of
all of them in such a short time.

603
00:48:29,990 --> 00:48:33,660
It's a relief that the case
isn't in the spotlight anymore.

604
00:48:34,286 --> 00:48:36,997
She's so elated
that he got what he deserved.

605
00:48:37,080 --> 00:48:40,167
If she hears about the video on the news…

606
00:48:42,336 --> 00:48:44,087
She'll be utterly shocked.

607
00:48:45,172 --> 00:48:48,258
For her sake, there shouldn't be
any follow-up articles

608
00:48:48,342 --> 00:48:50,677
that draw attention to this case again.

609
00:48:51,720 --> 00:48:52,679
You're right.

610
00:48:53,764 --> 00:48:55,349
We can't have that happen.

