00:50:55,010 --> 00:50:58,764
Since your mother is meeting
her friends this evening,

625
00:50:59,473 --> 00:51:01,683
how about you and I go out for dinner?

626
00:51:04,144 --> 00:51:06,021
I see. You already have plans?

627
00:51:08,148 --> 00:51:08,982
With a friend?

628
00:51:09,691 --> 00:51:10,817
Okay.

629
00:51:10,901 --> 00:51:11,985
Have fun.

630
00:51:12,068 --> 00:51:13,487
I'll see you at home.

631
00:51:14,154 --> 00:51:15,572
Okay. Bye.

