00:51:19,075 --> 00:51:20,118
A friend?

633
00:51:30,921 --> 00:51:34,216
Welcome to Youngsan,
a city full of love and happiness.

634
00:51:52,651 --> 00:51:54,528
YOUNGSAN CHILDREN'S HOME

635
00:51:54,611 --> 00:51:55,737
Seung-ho.

636
00:51:57,447 --> 00:52:01,159
I asked you last time
not to show up like this.

637
00:52:04,246 --> 00:52:05,413
Do you not like me?

638
00:52:07,582 --> 00:52:08,416
Why not?

639
00:52:10,710 --> 00:52:12,212
Seung-ho, you see…

640
00:52:13,880 --> 00:52:17,467
I've never thought of you
to be more than Seung-hee's brother.

641
00:52:26,017 --> 00:52:27,936
So I'm asking you. Please.

642
00:52:32,482 --> 00:52:33,900
Don't come here again.

643
00:52:44,202 --> 00:52:45,370
Bye.

644
00:52:48,123 --> 00:52:49,457
Kim Jae-eun.

645
00:52:55,589 --> 00:52:57,799
Seung-ho, please let go of me.

646
00:52:58,508 --> 00:52:59,342
Okay?

