00:53:17,694 --> 00:53:19,362
ON DUTY FOR YOUR SAFETY AND HAPPINESS
YOUNGSAN POLICE STATION

648
00:53:30,040 --> 00:53:31,374
Hey, kid.

649
00:53:31,458 --> 00:53:33,209
Is something wrong? Do you need help?

650
00:53:35,003 --> 00:53:37,964
Hey, is that blood on your clothes?

651
00:53:45,388 --> 00:53:46,431
Hey!

652
00:53:54,356 --> 00:53:55,815
I'd like an apology.

653
00:53:57,776 --> 00:53:59,986
And please stay away from me.

654
00:54:05,825 --> 00:54:06,743
Pardon?

655
00:54:06,826 --> 00:54:08,870
Boys can be like that

656
00:54:09,371 --> 00:54:12,832
when they like someone.

657
00:54:14,000 --> 00:54:15,919
And I'll be blunt.

658
00:54:16,002 --> 00:54:18,129
Nothing really happened.

659
00:54:18,213 --> 00:54:20,632
You just scraped your palms and knees.

660
00:54:20,715 --> 00:54:21,549
That's…

661
00:54:23,218 --> 00:54:24,552
That's because I ran away.

662
00:54:24,636 --> 00:54:26,054
If I hadn't, I would have…

663
00:54:28,306 --> 00:54:29,182
Here.

664
00:54:30,016 --> 00:54:31,977
Take this, okay?

665
00:54:32,060 --> 00:54:36,606
I understand that you're hurt
and upset right now,

666
00:54:36,690 --> 00:54:39,901
But can you just pretend
that you briefly went out

667
00:54:39,985 --> 00:54:42,737
with a law student
from Seoul National University?

668
00:54:42,821 --> 00:54:43,947
Let me go.

669
00:54:47,158 --> 00:54:48,243
I'll…

670
00:54:48,785 --> 00:54:52,205
I'll get you a scholarship
to Gyeongji University.

671
00:54:52,789 --> 00:54:56,167
My husband's aunt is the chairwoman there.

672
00:54:59,838 --> 00:55:03,008
How will you pay your tuition

673
00:55:03,091 --> 00:55:05,051
when you don't have parents?

674
00:55:05,844 --> 00:55:08,722
I'll make sure you get that scholarship.

675
00:55:08,805 --> 00:55:13,393
So let's not make a big deal
out of nothing, okay?

676
00:55:24,529 --> 00:55:25,447
I'll…

677
00:55:26,281 --> 00:55:28,324
take the scholarship then.

678
00:55:29,534 --> 00:55:30,577
Okay.

679
00:55:31,161 --> 00:55:33,538
I'll make sure you get it.

680
00:55:34,789 --> 00:55:35,832
The scholarship.

681
00:55:47,844 --> 00:55:48,845
Kim Jae-eun.

682
00:55:56,644 --> 00:55:57,771
Don't be mistaken.

683
00:55:59,272 --> 00:56:01,608
It's not like I actually liked you.

684
00:56:02,734 --> 00:56:05,236
If you needed money,
you should have just said so.

685
00:56:06,529 --> 00:56:07,989
You pathetic orphan.

