with a law student
from Seoul National University?

689
00:56:40,480 --> 00:56:41,314
Jin Seung-ho.

690
00:56:51,866 --> 00:56:53,451
Twenty years ago,

691
00:56:56,371 --> 00:56:57,872
the day my life was

692
00:56:58,748 --> 00:57:01,251
turned upside down
for the very first time…

