00:57:04,587 --> 00:57:05,797
You killed him.

694
00:57:07,257 --> 00:57:08,341
You murderer.

695
00:57:13,555 --> 00:57:16,432
My Seung-ho…

696
00:57:19,102 --> 00:57:22,856
My poor baby…

697
00:57:25,024 --> 00:57:29,195
My goodness, Seung-ho…

